<h1> You're <strong>almost</strong> done with registering for the festival..."</h1>

<div class="alert alert-success">
  <p>
    Please check your Email-Account for an Email we sent you. You have to klick the link in the Email to confirm your registration. If you don't do that you are not registered.
  </p>
  <p>You registered with the data:</p>
    <% @data.each do |key, value| %> 
    <p><%="#{key}: #{value}"%></p>
    <% end %>
  <p>
    To change something go to <a href="http://www.example.com">update</a>.
  </p>
  </p>
    To register another person repeat the <%= link_to("registration-process", root_path) %>.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="alert alert-danger">
  <p>
    If you didn't get an email most probably you made a typo in the email-adress. Hit the backwards-button of the browser to correct your input and submit again or just repeat the <%= link_to("registration-process", root_path) %> completely.
    
    If the email-address is definitely right, write an email to ...
  </p>
</div>